arts.ttl: Banned Bellamy's fire still burns in Liechtenstein
arts.sum: Banned Wales boss Craig Bellamy will have to watch Saturday's World Cup qualifier in Liechtenstein from the stands, having been suspended as a player when they were last in Vaduz.

arts.ttl: Can you name Wales XI from 2009 win in Liechtenstein?
arts.sum: As Wales return to Vaduz on Saturday can you name the side that won a World Cup qualifier 2-0 in Liechtenstein 16 years ago under John Toshack?

arts.ttl: Liechtenstein vs Wales predictions: Welsh can seal high-scoring success
arts.sum: Liechtenstein face Wales in World Cup qualifying Group J on Saturday and Dan Childs anticipates a convincing victory for the away team.

arts.ttl: Liechtenstein vs Wales - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Saturday's World Cup Qualifying - Europe clash between Liechtenstein and Wales, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
